 108:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Initializes the RCC extended peripherals clocks according to the specified
 109:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   *         parameters in the RCC_PeriphCLKInitTypeDef.
 110:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   * @param  PeriphClkInit: pointer to an RCC_PeriphCLKInitTypeDef structure that
 111:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****   *         contains the configuration information for the Extended Peripherals clocks
